data.description: Energy Efficient solar panels included!!Great solid built rambler home with 1200+ sq. ft, all on one level, 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Open floor plan kitchen with island, lots of cabinets for storage, stainless steel appliances, with newer dishwasher and garbage disposal, all included. Vaulted ceilings in the living room. Primary suite with bathroom and walking closet. Large fenced in backyard for your garden or just to hang out and relax. Great size attached 2 car garage. Very low power bill. No HOA fees. This is a must see home!!!
